</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="http://ksgfaculty.harvard.edu/Samantha_Power" class="external text" title="http://ksgfaculty.harvard.edu/Samantha_Power" rel="nofollow">Power's profile</a> at Harvard</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pbs.org/now/politics/power.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pbs.org/now/politics/power.html" rel="nofollow">Samantha Power: Biography</a> | <a href="/wiki/PBS" title="PBS" class="mw-redirect">PBS</a></li>
